OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOrkney
OL,6,Fstaying dry through the day, but a few
OL,7,Flight well scattered showers affecting
OL,8,FShetland. Some late sunshine then
OL,9,Fclear spells. Northerly winds fresh
OL,10,Facross Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,13,Fweather in prospect with most dry with
OL,14,Foccasional brighter spells developing.
OL,15,FWinds northeasterly and relatively
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
