OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fchange to more unsettled conditions
OL,7,Fwith a series of rain bands crossing
OL,8,Ffrom the south. However, with winds
OL,9,Fstaying southwesterly temperatures a
OL,10,Flittle up on the seasonal averages.
